===Proper noun===
'''Sindhi'''

#An Indo-Aryan language spoken in four main dialects in [[Pakistan]]. There are around 35 million Sindhi speakers in Sindh and more than 40 million thoughout the world. Sindhi is written with a modified Arabic script that has 52 letters.

